            "id": "NCT07015931",
            "title": "Efficacy of 0.025% Retinoic Acid Cream Compared to 0.1% Adapalene Cream on Mild Acne Vulgaris, as Well as Safety Profile and Post-Acne Sequelae in Fitzpatrick Skin Types III-V: A Randomized Double-Blind Clinical Trial Using the Split-Face Method",
